AutoCloseable, Clob, NClob
public class AutoCloseNClob
extends DelegatingNClob<NClob>
implements AutoCloseable, NClob

An AutoCloseable NClob. When the automatic resource management block construct invokes close(), DelegatingClob.free() will be called on the underlying NClob.
